title: How Badly Do I Want a Titan?
description: Probably not badly enough to put in the work to get one… but I’ll get to that.  First, why am I even asking the question? We were on a fleet back during the invasion of Insmother where Asher Elias, leader of the Imperium and one time commander of the Reavers SIG, was answering some questions […]
author: Wilhelm Arcturus
